| S2-02 | search-filters | C2-02 | filter/facet query | 只读 | `4-1/task-99` |
| S2-03 | saved-search-sheet | C2-03 | saved search CRUD | saved_searches | `4-1/task-100` |
| S2-04 | search-empty | C2-01 | empty result state | 只读 | `4-1/task-101` |
